1 c. a country or government identified on any sanctions
2 list of the United State Department of the Treasury's
3 Office of Foreign Assets Control;
4 5. 8. "Land" means the same as defined in Section 6 of this
5 title, but shall not include oil, gas, other minerals, or any
6 interest therein.
7 9. "Military installation" means a base, camp, post, station,
8 yard, or center that is under the jurisdiction of the Department of
